  "shortCode": "DXZX5pHkVHt",
  "caption": "This started with AI\n\n…which sounds impressive\nuntil you actually think about what that means\n\nBecause starting the video is easy\nAI can do that part\n\nBut what happens after\nis where things change\n\nWhen something gets pulled apart\nrebuilt from scratch\nadjusted over and over\nuntil it finally feels right\n\nis that still AI\n\nor just a convenient label\n\nBecause the real reason this works\nhas nothing to do with how it started\n\nit’s why you didn’t leave\n\nYou were supposed to\n\nMost sites don’t get a second chance\nthey get a glance\nand that’s it\n\nBut this one held you\njust long enough\n\nand that’s intentional\n\nGood websites don’t just look clean\nthey control attention\n\nthey disrupt привычة\nthey create friction in the scroll\n\nthey make you stop\neven when you didn’t plan to\n\nAnd once that happens\nyou’re already deeper than you meant to go\n\nSo yeah\n“AI made this” sounds good\n\nit just leaves out the part that actually matters\n\n#webdesigner #webdev #uxdesign #design #openclaw",
